metadata.title: God Bless You | Stand Up Comedy | Ft  @AnubhavSinghBassi
metadata.description:
Hanji toh covid 2021 ke dauraan apna birthday celebrate kiya tha toh uske baare mei hi bataya hai.. aur bhi bhot kuch hua tha lockdown mei mere sath toh uske liye poori video dekhna baaki aap log bhi batana comments mei apne crazy experiences lockdown ke comments section mei!! cheers!

Edited by: Snehit Bansal
Sound: Srijith Menon 
Venue Courtesy: The Laugh Store India


Join the be_a_bassi email list for all the early updates for live shows, new videos, merchandise etc., and register Karlo shab
